title: (BONUS EP) Crimes Caught on Tape
description:
This week, the gals hit rewind on some creepy cases captured on camera. Topics include some Google Earth breakthroughs, a shipping container from hell, and the problem with biometric data. Bust open a bottle of Evil Eye Red Blend, don't forget to hit record, and tune in for Crimes Caught on Tape.

For a full list of show sponsors, visit www.wineandcrimepodcast.com/support
